<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l16">fıel vns wol daʒ Jr eẅch mıt <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wol dauon </del> mıt den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l17"><expan>ſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅrs teıls wol <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>redt</expan> vnd eẅr <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> deſt <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l18">den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> tag geſchıkt hett / wan vns dunkt daʒ ſıch von <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen </ab>
