<ab facs="#facs_584_r2l20">auf dıſʒ ʒeıt von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache . niht <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> in gut </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_584" id="291r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Strasb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, von Costencz und von
                                <expan>Essling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan> und <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> dreyn
                                <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>yed<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>cetula<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusam</expan>
